.panel-heading
  h3 Earn #{number_to_currency(@business.active_referral_token.amount_in_cents / 100, precision: 0)} for every new member you refer

.panel-body.p-t-0.m-b-1
  .m-b-2
    | Get a colleague to join our community as either a new specialist or business member and earn #{number_to_currency(@business.active_referral_token.amount_in_cents / 100, precision: 0)} for your account when they set up their free profile.

  .row.m-b-2(data-controller="clipboard")
    .col-xs-12
      .form-group
        input.form-control.input-lg(data-target="clipboard.source" value=referrals_url(token: @business.active_referral_token.token))
    .col-xs-12
      button.btn.btn-primary.btn-sm.btn-block.clipboard-button(data-action="clipboard#copy") Copy Link

  .m-b-2
    h4
      | Accrued Credit: #{number_to_currency(@business.referral_credits_in_cents / 100)}
